description.@value: 調査報告における地図作成上の説明、ペルシャ語の名前の意味、東ペルシア産の岩石の地質学的考察など、調査にまつわる地理学的・地質学的考察を含む。

Vol. 2: Includes an explanation of the maps that accompanied the expedition report; an explanation of the meaning of various Persian names; the geology of the mountains of eastern Iran; and a general discussion of the geological aspects of the expedition.
